data.description: Spacious 4 bedroom and 2.5 bathroom home in desirable Sorrento subdivision at Riviera Isles. Cozy, immaculate home with a light, bright and airy feeling. Open Kitchen concept and light wood kitchen cabinetry making perfect for entertainment and family enjoyment. Private paved patio area with a 6' privacy fenced, best of all no neighbors to the back or to the side.. instead enjoy a perfectly located playground with for your little ones. Community has plenty to offer with a resort style pool, tennis, basketball courts, gym, kids playground area and much more. Great School Zones and close to shopping and restaurants.
